{"tid":1600950,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔頭損左 求救","createTime":"2019-09-28T22:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T23:16:51.000Z","uid":27477,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf806c6b1fa2203799a1c0231af20f88085b76d","tid":1600950,"uid":27477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"隻貓仔琴日先到，個半月大，唔知係咪熟悉新環境/同佢玩時撞損左個頭，眼對上位置<br />\n上網望左下，有人話用棉花球印一印再查抗菌藥膏，有人話用好小好小量滴露開水用棉花球印（我唔太敢）<br />\n依加有冇話用邊隻藥膏消毒好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgYmizp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgYmizp.jpg&h=ba454540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外見佢R耳後都R得幾密 但表面望落唔見有明顯傷痕<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCRK0Oy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCRK0Oy.jpg&h=be45027b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依加打算轉頭早少少出去寵物用品鋪望下有冇野幫到佢"},{"pid":"a67c5055d05bb7a8e2f27f708017f37bbd0256c1","tid":1600950,"uid":47647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T22:19:56.000Z","msg":"用神仙水啦，同埋新貓都有可能有「室」架<br />\n杜蟲個啲都要做足"},{"pid":"7d95919f8734f3ec0b279e25cc64ad3a15cb10a1","tid":1600950,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T22:22:53.000Z","msg":"答案係貓頭鷹"},{"pid":"db04a7e2f0753dceedd41cbacfda55a0b95000e7","tid":1600950,"uid":27477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T22:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://g.search.alicdn.com/img/bao/uploaded/i4/i2/636785375/TB2DsShgL2H8KJjy0FcXXaDlFXa_!!636785375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.search.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fbao%2Fuploaded%2Fi4%2Fi2%2F636785375%2FTB2DsShgL2H8KJjy0FcXXaDlFXa_%21%21636785375.jpg&h=381b6dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪呢隻? 係嘅我晏就出去搵下"},{"pid":"4a31cd5577c448eaa2a400f943dc93af1631a897","tid":1600950,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T22:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3526ecc